    {
      "id": "PopularPost192818",
      "post_content": "If the first part had been \"Add ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) to your mana pool\" the charm would have been no better or worse, but it would have been a fantastic collector's item. \"They printed Dark Rit, Lightning Bolt, and Giant Growth all on one card!\"  \n  \n(I suggest Dark Rit makes more sense because those three cards were part of the very first cycle to exist in Magic: the Gathering, the \"get three of something for one mana\" cycle that also included [Ancestral Recall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ancestral Recall).)",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost192818\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">If the first part had been \"Add <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> to your mana pool\" the charm would have been no better or worse, but it would have been a fantastic collector's item. \"They printed Dark Rit, Lightning Bolt, and Giant Growth all on one card!\"<br/><br/>(I suggest Dark Rit makes more sense because those three cards were part of the very first cycle to exist in Magic: the Gathering, the \"get three of something for one mana\" cycle that also included <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ancestral Recall\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ancestral Recall\">Ancestral Recall</a>.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '192818'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (9/1/2011 3:11:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\