      "id": "PopularPost9438",
      "post_content": "[Raise Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raise Dead), [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt) and [Giant Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth) combined into one instant that costs the sum of them . . . . its ok, but when you really need to consider whether its worth paying three man for a spell that usually costs one mana, just for the convenience of choice.",
